    <div class="container">
      <h1>Air Conditioning Repair in Downtown Lake Charles</h1>
      <p>Professional HVAC service for downtown businesses, offices, restaurants, and residences. Fast response and 24/7 emergency service.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <section class="content-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-main">
          <p class="lead"><strong>Downtown Lake Charles</strong> is the heart of our city—home to businesses, restaurants, entertainment venues, and a growing number of loft apartments and residences. Latour's HVAC provides fast, professional <strong>air conditioning repair</strong> and HVAC service to keep downtown comfortable for work and play.</p>

          <p>Whether you operate a restaurant on Ryan Street, manage an office building, or live in one of downtown's renovated loft spaces, reliable HVAC is essential. We understand the urgency of keeping your business comfortable and your customers happy.</p>

          <h2>HVAC Services for Downtown Lake Charles</h2>
          <p>We serve both commercial and residential customers in the downtown area:</p>

          <h3>Commercial HVAC Services</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Restaurant HVAC:</strong> Keep your kitchen ventilated and dining room comfortable</li>
            <li><strong>Office Building AC:</strong> Reliable cooling for productive work environments</li>
            <li><strong>Retail Store Climate Control:</strong> Comfortable shopping experiences for customers</li>
            <li><strong>Rooftop Unit Service:</strong> Repair and maintenance for RTUs common in commercial buildings</li>
            <li><strong>Commercial Refrigeration:</strong> Walk-in coolers and freezers for restaurants</li>
            <li><strong>Emergency Commercial Repair:</strong> 24/7 service to minimize business downtime</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Residential HVAC Services</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Loft Apartment AC:</strong> Solutions for open floor plans and high ceilings</li>
            <li><strong>Historic Building HVAC:</strong> Ductless and mini-split options for renovated spaces</li>
            <li><strong>AC Repair:</strong> Same-day service for residential cooling emergencies</li>
            <li><strong>Heat Pump Systems:</strong> Efficient heating and cooling for downtown living</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Why Downtown Businesses Trust Latour's</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Fast Response:</strong> We know downtime costs money—we respond quickly</li>
            <li><strong>After-Hours Service:</strong> Repairs when your business is closed to minimize disruption</li>
            <li><strong>Commercial Experience:</strong> We understand commercial HVAC systems and their demands</li>
            <li><strong>Maintenance Plans:</strong> Prevent breakdowns with regular commercial maintenance</li>
            <li><strong>24/7 Emergency Service:</strong> Because AC failures don't follow business hours</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>About Downtown Lake Charles</h2>
          <p>Downtown Lake Charles is experiencing a renaissance, with new restaurants, entertainment venues, and residential developments bringing renewed energy to the area. From the historic Charpentier District to the waterfront development along the lakefront, downtown offers a mix of historic charm and modern amenities.</p>

          <p>The area's mix of building types—from century-old structures to modern commercial buildings—requires HVAC expertise across a range of systems. Our technicians are experienced with both historic building challenges and modern commercial equipment.</p>

          <h2>Common Downtown HVAC Needs</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Restaurant Kitchen Ventilation:</strong> Make-up air and exhaust systems</li>
            <li><strong>High-Ceiling Cooling:</strong> Proper air distribution in tall spaces</li>
            <li><strong>Humidity Control:</strong> Critical for restaurants and retail</li>
            <li><strong>Rooftop Unit Maintenance:</strong> Keeping commercial RTUs running efficiently</li>
            <li><strong>Ductless Systems:</strong> Solutions for renovated historic buildings</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Schedule HVAC Service in Downtown Lake Charles</h2>
          <p>Keep your downtown business or residence comfortable. Call <a href="tel:+13375134425">(337) 513-4425</a> or <a href="/schedule-service/">schedule online</a>. We offer same-day service and 24/7 emergency response.</p>
